urls.description: Keep Essex Active is an Active Essex initiative to keep the residents of Essex healthy, with Essex instructors! The aim is to keep everyone moving despite the barriers they may be facing due to the COVID-19 pandemic. To reduce the risk of injury, never force or strain yourself. If at any point you feel pain, discomfort or dizziness, please stop your practice and rest. Only return to exercise when fully recovered. These sessions do not offer medical advice and should not substitute or replace professional medical advice.
